Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越了一萬兩千年的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四散的靈魂的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡集結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邁向結束的神話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正要迎來新的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聖合體 GO！ AQUARION！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion 為什麼禁忌的這個名字會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不行 搞什麼 這個合體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以往的常識和感覺都四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂了 一直珍藏的某種東西 爆發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然說Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦漿在顫動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預料之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就將你們變成灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個氣味的真正面目是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Evol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以Vector Z為頭部的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion竟然還有別的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的不潔 男女合體應該是禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由那些少年們的手裡解開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君 到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是在Aquarion的裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Evol是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 你在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快從那個男人身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶走並駕駛Aquarion的恐怖分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君不是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要狡辯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了 普通人的組合來當頭部什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官 司令部傳來的強制合體解除要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就在試了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊的控制一切都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然跟那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學園長　啊不 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同於現在的Aquaria樣的男女分開的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是雌雄同體的勝利之完全體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 神的道具人類怎麼能夠使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊這個傢伙  虛有其表嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出真正的實力上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abductor…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有那種武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明書上可沒寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小子…到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼能和Aquarion如此同步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等下你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那招是怎麼弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 自己就動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是因為荷爾蒙？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 好野性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 一個外行人居然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 既然解除不了合體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就靠身為頭部的你來戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭部？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 沒用的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要 沒辦法的 戰鬥什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不要這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被勉強進來的 出去也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 少女 這種狀況你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君 逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為「我們都是廢柴什麼的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方的增援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子不是雜魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大型機 同型號的三台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂大人 有回艦命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請和我們一起回Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲那個老頭子的指使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Neagula的採取已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這之後的戰鬥是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定是否戰鬥的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是等著被幹掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好了 我來教你戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將拉手上的鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡的Element能力異常地增幅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個小鬼共鳴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是男女機合體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同 和以往的Aquaria完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神 神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這群傢伙是來拖後腿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴間內訌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味 氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味的盡頭 有黑暗伴隨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把別的機體的部分強硬地接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣還有那種動作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝過野獸的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 這個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就一直哭個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是戰鬥中 別分神 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃 是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 能保護得了她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喪服的結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做過的惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結 結婚儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element能力 絕望之血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的影像刺激到腦部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個場景為什麼我們能看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奪回禁斷之名的Aquarion展示給我們看的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預知到的是這樣的情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕望而最糟的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那裡的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁邊的男人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把臉給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這氣味的元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都是你的錯 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行胡亂的合體 還牽扯進御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是你這混蛋的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 心跳加快 興奮不止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小一直被大家避諱著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那人置於不顧也是 這力量的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 決定不再使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我想要保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻讓御子乃經歷更加糟糕的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我這種人 要保護御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.08,0:17:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屏障等級低下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去Aquarion會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被神話認可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便是自身成為神話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔·空 你已擁有這份覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 「我們都是廢柴什麼的」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我這種人混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是剛見面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡力地想要保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會哭泣嗚咽的弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃的手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巧 纖細的 滑滑的 溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種加速度 不單是Aquarion的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即將到達衛星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 這是那少年的Element能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元之門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遺憾 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲 我還可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「還能戰鬥」開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喪家犬就老實地回自己狗窩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種瘦弱的男人 把御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著那小鬼和女孩歸艦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那男的 能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這女孩 沒有一點價值
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷登上Aquaria的人不能就這麼放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能等待著我 獨一無二的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那翱翔在天際的少年的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵人的傢伙回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Guniss毀壞成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有收穫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於我的可惡女人
