Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:52.23,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}片道分の勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:59.75,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}僕ら 悲劇を受け入れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:01.97,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}枯れた此処に
